@OReillySolid A10: The answer is always "depends".  #IoTChat

@OReillySolid  A7: Document everything. Reconfirm your BOM & margins.  Pick your partners. Have engineers on your team #IoTChat
@OReillySolid A8: You ask yourself some questions: Where are my customers? Where are my suppliers? What is the cost to ship?  #IoTChat

@OReillySolid A5: #1 Tip: Don't do it alone. You'll go in circles.  #IoTChat

  #IoTChat
